Package com.pranavpandey.android.dynamic.support.picker.color

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DynamicColorDialog
    A color picker dialog fragment to display multiple grids of colors and their shades.
    DynamicColorPicker
    A color picker inside a FrameLayout to display multiple grids of colors and their shades.
    DynamicColorPopup
    A PopupWindow to display a grid of colors.
    DynamicColorView
    A FrameLayout to display a color in different DynamicColorShape.
  • Annotation Types Summary 
    Annotation Type Description
    DynamicColorControl
    Interface to hold the color control constant values to provide color sliders accordingly.
    DynamicColorShape
    Interface to hold the color shape constant values to generate color swatches accordingly.
